---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import EmailCaptureForm from '@/components/EmailCaptureForm.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Career Captain — Your Starting Path | Flight School Friend"
  description="You need a structured, cost-aware career training plan. Here's your recommended roadmap from PPL through ATP."
  noindex
>
  <section class="bg-white max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Your Recommended Path</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">Career Captain</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-4 font-medium">You need a structured, cost-aware career training plan.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">This is a starting recommendation, not a final training decision.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Roadmap Timeline -->
    <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12 overflow-x-auto">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">Roadmap Timeline</h3>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-center text-xs font-medium text-slate-700 min-w-max">
        <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">Medical First</div>
        <span class="text-slate-300">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">Budget/Finance Plan</div>
        <span class="text-slate-300">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">141/Academy/Fast 61</div>
        <span class="text-slate-300">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">PPL</div>
        <span class="text-slate-300">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">IR</div>
        <span class="text-slate-300">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">Commercial</div>
        <span class="text-slate-300">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">CFI</div>
        <span class="text-slate-300">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="bg-sky-600 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-sm">ATP Path</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Why this fits:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-sky-500 font-bold">✓</span> You are likely evaluating aviation as a serious career path.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-sky-500 font-bold">✓</span> Training sequence, financing, timeline, and medical eligibility matter early.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-sky-500 font-bold">✓</span> A structured program may help if you need speed, financing, or a full-path plan.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-sky-500 font-bold">✓</span> You should understand the full path beyond private pilot before committing.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">What to clarify next:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">?</span> Can you qualify medically for the certificate class you need?</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">?</span> Do you understand the full training cost through commercial/CFI?</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">?</span> Are you looking for full-time or part-time training?</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">?</span> Do you need financing, school structure, or airline pathway options?</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <EmailCaptureForm quizSegment="career_captain" />

    <div class="mb-12 border-t border-slate-200 pt-12">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Related Resources</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/guides/flight-school-cost/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition">Flight School Cost Guide</a>
        <a href="/guides/part-61-vs-part-141/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition">Part 61 vs Part 141</a>
        <a href="/guides/how-to-choose-a-flight-school/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition">How to Choose a Flight School</a>
        <a href="/guides/private-pilot-requirements/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition">Private Pilot Requirements</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="text-sky-600 font-medium hover:underline flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path></svg>
        Retake the Quiz
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
